    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ADVENTURE MODE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/e9ede97b90d5320e4658769e77b7b17a.poster.avif?t=1762892753\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/e9ede97b90d5320e4658769e77b7b17a.webm?t=1762892753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/e9ede97b90d5320e4658769e77b7b17a.mp4?t=1762892753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your journey to unravel the mysteries of the ooze spreading throughout the Voxisles takes you through meticulously handcrafted islands brimming with quirky characters, dangerous monsters, challenging puzzles, and – true to the name – epic adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NEW - PROCEDURAL SURVIVAL ISLANDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/34fb587c52645dfdc27089d437bd6259.poster.avif?t=1762892753\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/34fb587c52645dfdc27089d437bd6259.webm?t=1762892753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/34fb587c52645dfdc27089d437bd6259.mp4?t=1762892753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You start with nothing, so pick up some sticks and get started. Loot crumbling ruins, fulfill strange quests, build ladders and bridges and bases, craft and upgrade ever-more-potent equipment, and challenge powerful bosses to cleanse each unique, procedurally-generated isle of the ooze.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check out the procedural survival worlds demo today!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEFEAT &amp; DESTROY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/9fbf74d36982ee9a5a22825dcc83b675.poster.avif?t=1762892753\" width=800 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/9fbf74d36982ee9a5a22825dcc83b675.webm?t=1762892753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/9fbf74d36982ee9a5a22825dcc83b675.mp4?t=1762892753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Experience a unique combination of crafting, RPG progression, and first-person shooting. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft or loot an impressive arsenal of firearms, melee weapons, and magical spells to defeat the mutated wildlife that roam these lands, from persistent little blobs of ooze to divebombing birds, from armed and angry skeletons to rocket-launching robots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With dynamic material-based destruction, towers, trees and terrain crumble alongside the carnage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRAFT &amp; BUILD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/cb7aae19fe78af215c4524da021db8df.poster.avif?t=1762892753\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/cb7aae19fe78af215c4524da021db8df.webm?t=1762892753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/cb7aae19fe78af215c4524da021db8df.mp4?t=1762892753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Voxile’s crafting system combines 50 materials and dozens of other resources into weapons, workbenches, bags, boots, food and flak jackets and jackhammers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a variety of tools and contraptions to solve problems your own way. Create stairs, scaffolds, and ladders to reach new heights. Build a base, and decorate it however you like – everything you see in the world can eventually be broken down and crafted anew.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CREATE YOUR OWN ISLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/29e3eaa5ee823ed034d2b8f0fe112ac1.poster.avif?t=1762892753\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/29e3eaa5ee823ed034d2b8f0fe112ac1.webm?t=1762892753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/29e3eaa5ee823ed034d2b8f0fe112ac1.mp4?t=1762892753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Our in-game editor empowers you to design your own islands, complete with your own unique gameplay and quests. Joyful to use, with seamless MagicaVoxel integration, an intuitive world editor, and a surprisingly powerful built-in scripting system for charting out a new adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on your adventure solo, or join forces with friends in four-player multiplayer (co-op optional).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And you can talk to both dogs AND cats. Now in Early Access.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/4d18b60e20378f3729708f26bc804940.poster.avif?t=1762892753\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/4d18b60e20378f3729708f26bc804940.webm?t=1762892753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283580/extras/4d18b60e20378f3729708f26bc804940.mp4?t=1762892753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>",
